	<h1 class="title">我们发现，如果你坐地铁没带手机你一定会干这些事 | 好奇心研究所</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1288/small/1288.gif?1404690740" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡昱 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-02 08:20:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15225/medium/15225.jpg?1442840512" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15225" data-title="《我们发现，如果你坐地铁没带手机你一定会干这些事 | 好奇心研究所》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15225/medium/15225.jpg?1442840512" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15225.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
